Hamichi is here to tey and calm down from being so stressed

Superbia was walking around, hoping to spot a new victim, she looked quite bored until she spotted Hamachi *Oh, intresting !* she rubbed her hands and approached her "Well, well, *well*, who do we have here ?~"
She noticed her and jumped back, tail rattling as she hissed "***Go away.***"
She cackled, putting a hand on Hamachi's shoulder "Oh, *darling* , it's going to take more than some useless threat to make me go away"
She tried to bite her
She took her hand away, disgusted "Oh please *darling* have some manners! " Slowly, a humanoid moth creature appeared behind her
She hissed again "I told you to leave me alone." Her own stand appeared
"Oh, it's not happening *any* time soon, *Darling*" Her stand launched itself towards Hamachi, putting two of its four hands on her hand
She yelped and tried to get away

The stand was firmly grabbing her, looking at her right in the eyes. Meanwhile, Superbia was cackling loudly "Try as hard as you wish, *you can't escape her grasp* "
Suddenly, a thick, white, mist surrounded Hamachi, like a sudden flash of light
She was starting to panic

For a bit, Hamachi could barely see, but soon enough, her vision was back to normal. 
All around her was white, just pure white, giving off an otherworldly vibe.
She didnt like this. She was starting to freak out

Hamachi was alone in the Mist, nothing was around, not even the stand that attacked her earlier. 
After a while, she could see a shilouette in the distance... it was the only other thing in this vast white nothingness.
She narrowed her eyes and jogged towards the figure

As she got closer, she could see the figure was familiar... *very* familiar. 
In the mist, she could see it was a *Sarcio*. He was just... standing here, speechless
"SARCIO!!!!" She called out happy to see him "Oh thank goodness you're ok! Guess the antidote was found huh?"
'Sarcio' smiled, and put a hand on Hamachi's shoulder, his hand was... colder than normal. "It did ! I'm so happy to see you too, Hamachi !"
She shuddered a bit at that but shrugged it off, tail wagging "Nowww that you're better I can introduce you to be friend Nexum!!!!"
"Oh, a friend? that's great !" He smiled softly, getting closer to her, his breath was also cold... almost freezing "Well, let's go meet her !"
She shuddered again "Are....you ok???? You're oddly cold...."
"Oh, don't worry about me ! I'm still a bit sick from the poison..." He caughed, losing his Balance a bit.
She got worried and tried to help him stay steady "Alright....."
He kept caughing, louder and louder... some blood seemed to be dripping from his mouth "I'm fine... *I'm fine*" he was trying to catch his breath, almost falling
"Y-Youre not!!! L-lets get you help right away!!!" She tried to get him to a hospital
There was nothing around, just the wide emptiness of The Mist, Sarcio kept caughing, and ended falling on the ground, putting his face in his hand. "Ha...Hamachi" he muttered
She began to tear up "Fu-fuck I-I need to....Call for help!!" But she has no phone.
He was pulling on Hamachi's Jacket, his voice was weak and his touch as cold as the dead. "hama....chi" His face was still in his hand.
Hamichi began to cry "Please h-hold on!" She tried to lift him up

Sarcio stoped her, and took his hand off his face. He was looking directly at Hamachi. 
His eyes were dead, his skin as pale as a ghost, it was almost like his whole face was melting, it's like he was just a gross and malformed version of himself now. *"Why...Hamachi"*
//wait is Sarcio here?
((it's not him, it's an illusion created by Superbia!
She screamed, starting to full on sob "Nonononononononono-"

Soon enough, Sarcio's face disapeared in The Mist, and Hamachi was alone yet again. 
Maniacal laughters echoed through the white nothingness.
//o h
She curled up, sobbing loudly

A familiar voice could be heard, it was faint, but hamachi could hear it 
"Hamachi..." It wasn't Sarcio's voice, it *couldn't* be, it had a higher pitch, like the one of a younger mun
Her ears perked up and she looked around frantically
She could see the silouhette of a shorter mun from afar, a *very* familiar one. It waved to her
"....N-Nexum....?" She got up and went over
"Hamachi ! " she smiled, it was a bit of a creepy smile, but that wasn't out of the ordinary for her
She began to run to her "Nexum!! Im so glad to see you ..."
"Me too ! I saw Sarcio and was hoping to see you !" Strangely, it seemed that Nexum wasn't with her stand
".....Wheres.....Duvet....?" She tilted her head
Nexum looked her dead in the eyes "Oh, Duvet ? He's busy right now, don't worry !"
"You....are usually always on him....." She was worried a bit
"It's ok! don't worry !" she kept her creepy, slightly uncanny smile up
She was starting to get a bit scared

"Oh, What's wrong Hamachi ? are you scared ? anxious ? are you fearing for your pathetic little life ?" her head was tilted, still in a smile, and the last words echoed through the Mist, with a different voice
She backed up "_You arent Nexum._"
"What ? didn't you miss me ? and am I wrong Hamachi ? *Am I* ?" she got closer
"**YOU. ARENT. NEXUM!**" She yelled, turning on her heels and trying to run away

'Nexum' didn't ran after her. And soon enough, Hamachi was running in circles. 
"There's no escape, it's useless Hamachi" She said, calmy, through her creepy smile
"**I DONT CARE IF ITS USELESS I REFUSE TO BACK DOWN.**"

'Nexum' just sat down. Silent. Looking at Hamachi runing around
A loud cackled could be heard in the Mist, *"Useless, it's all useless *darling*"
"**Superbia.**" She hissed "SHOW YOURSELF COWARD!"

"my my, it would just *ruin* the show, don't you think ?" 
Nexum was nowhere to be seen.
"Your show is already ruined. I know what I'm seeing is fake now."

*"Very Well"* 
A new silouhette appeared, far away. *"Come and get me"*
She hissed and tried to run towards her

The Silouhette was just standing, smiling at her, it was *superbia*. 
She didn't even moved, and just kept her smile as she was running towards her
She summoned her stand and tried to attack her
She dodged it with ease, even putting a finger on hamachi's nose "*pathetic little creature*"
(( @Pastel warrior of hope!!!
She growled and tried ti bite her finger

She managed to bite her, but it seemed that it didn't affect her... no wound could be seen
She moved her finger from left to right "no, no, *no*, don't go to such *low* level, biting, really ? what are you ? a rabid animal ? Come on, *Darling*, you can do better~"
"Shut up. You arent even real are you." She growled
"Well, you'll have to find out yourself" She cackled an sigh, before staring right in Hamachi's eyes *"you're in **my** land now, Hamachi. **My** rules"*
She hissed at her "Fool me once shame on me. Fool me twice shame on you."
"Aw, how *cute* " She patted Hamachi's head "Good luck finding me out there !~" And just like that, she vanished in a chuckle
She growled and tried to find some way ti escape
Superbia's voice echoed through the Mist "It's useless, only *I* can let you escape"
She growled and sat there on the ground. "Then I simply wont play your stupid game."
She appeared in front of her, sword in hands, pointing *right* in between Hamachi's eyes "Aw, what a shame, If I had some more fun, I would've *considered* to spare you, oh well"
"Kill me then. Go ahead. Not like anyone will care." She stared at her, gripping the sword with her hand
"Oh, so you are *this* willing to die ? do you crave death that much ? you won't even fight back? " She moving the sword enough to start cutting Hamachi's hand a little
"Ive craved death ever since I was old enough to think on my own. But the cult never let me die. I was their 'God'." She rolled her eyez
She instantly retrieved her sword "Very well then, if death is what you want, it'll just e *boring* to give it to you, don't you think, *darling* ?"
She stared blankly at her "Coward."

She slowly started to fade "Oh trust me, *I'm no coward*" right before disapearing fully, she snapped her fingers 
Suddenly, the mist turned pure, dark *black*
She yelped in suprise, looming aroubd
*looking around
From the dark depth of the nothingness, a few shadows came, they were multiple, and soon enough, they were surrounding Hamachi, *chanting*
"No.....I-It cant be....NO! NOT AGAIN!" She stood up and tried to get past them "Nonononono-"

More and more figures started to appear, the chanting getting louder and louder 
It was like She as drowning in a sea of hooded figures, and some even grabbed her arms, looking directly in her eyes
She screames and began kicking. Her head hurt. Her head hurt so much. She felt like she was going to pass out

Her screams were drowned out by the chanting, the figures were barely affected by her kicking. What was before incoherent chanting slowly became more distinct, *they were chanting her name* over and over and over again
She felt tears streaming down her face before she passed out. Her heart felt like it was going to burst

Superbia cackled madly *god this was easy*. 
In a fraction of second, the figures were gone, and the Mist was no more. She approached Hamachi and whispered in her ear *"I hope I'll see you again, darling"* before walking away, humming.
She didn't have as much *fun* with her stand in such a long time.
Shes out cold, just laying on the ground
and superbia went on her to wherever the *fuck* she want
